1. to have colors for commands
   such as Grep and ls
2. to have keyboard shortcuts enabled such as
   CTRL-S
3. to have no typoAutoCorrection for my typos, since it is not
   100% accurate
4. If I close my shell, I want to close background processes
   automatically.
5. If I close my shell and all windows are open, I want to have them
   open the next time too in my shell. Therefore, I use Screen.


This file does NOT contain
1. coding settigs
2. Tab completions
3. small shell apps
4. fixes for specific OS


